            <abstract>
                <p>The story told in the Miracle is very similar to that of <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3664Miracle">Miracle of Mary: Miracle of the flight of Egypt; Miracle of the sycomore of Dabra Mǝṭmāq</ref>, 
                but the wording is different, and it is contained in a much smaller number of manuscripts. In 
